{"tid":705523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[補貼大灣區交通費]譚志源倡本港學生享(買)暑假無限次任搭膠鐵套票","createTime":"2018-06-17T08:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T13:06:21.000Z","uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"70a8576c89b2ab479bdf1226988fd1017514f893","tid":705523,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T08:32:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1402148-20180617.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1402148-20180617.htm&d=RfqEjC4p9oIoQvPbz36vO6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=0e79474d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1402148-20180617.htm&h=afaac8ae\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1402148-20180617.htm</a><br />\n譚志源倡本港學生享暑假無限次任搭高鐵套票<br />\n2018-06-17 HKT 11:22<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1402148_1_20180617112826.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1402148_1_20180617112826.jpg&h=4f0b0908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政制及🇨🇳🇨🇳內地🇨🇳🇨🇳事務局前局長、現任港區人大代表譚志源認為，青年人應多考慮香港以外的發展空間，例如粵港澳大灣區。他在本台節目《舊日的足跡》表示，香港青年應放下包袱，持開放態度，嘗試到大灣區參與暑假實習或一些短期課程。<br />\n<br />\n譚志源說，已向中央及省市政府建議，補貼市民來回大灣區及香港的交通費。<br />\n<br />\n在加強兩地青年交流方面，譚志源向中央提議，香港大學生乘搭高鐵到內地旅遊，可購買學生自遊行票，在暑假無限次任搭高鐵。他表示，已向港鐵主席及行政總裁提及有關建議，並獲他們支持。<br />\n<br />\n港台clickbait標題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff12e787b349391caceb186d99c29157d16a267","tid":705523,"uid":186692,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T08:36:23.000Z","msg":"自己阻住外資過嚟香港 之後就迫人去大灣區<br />\n呢個政府態度真係夠開放(ﾟ3ﾟ)～♪ (ﾟ3ﾟ)～♪"},{"pid":"9ffb24ad9db2cb8dda1deca7b7bf4545f5fa7209","tid":705523,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T10:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e23f100b86bc1948b749f5464c4b0b202b66803","tid":705523,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T13:06:21.000Z","msg":"死左點算， 係咪送埋一站式保險兼骨灰位一個"}]}